high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the sink and walk to the counter ahead.
Open the lower right cabinet, pick up the clear container inside and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the black fridge ahead.
Put the container inside the fridge on the top shelf, chill it for seven seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink to the right.
Open the lower left cabinet, put the chilled container inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled container in a cabinet.

Put the tray into the fridge and remove it

Put the tray into the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Place the tray in the fridge then put it in the cabinet

high_descs: Turn around and hang a left at the sink to face the cabinets under the counter.
Open the lower right cabinet, pick up a clear container from inside and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the black fridge on your left.
Put the container inside the fridge on the top left side of the shelf, chill it for seven seconds, remove it, and close the door.
Turn around and hang a right at the stool to reach the cabinets under the sink.
Open the lower left cabinet under the sink, put the chilled container inside and close the door.
